OL,5, Bosses of Britain's biggest companies  
OL,6, will have made more money in 2024 by   
OL,7, lunchtime on Thursday than the typical 
OL,8, worker will all year, research claims. 
OL,10,FBy 13:00 GMT, the pay of FTSE 100      
OL,11,Fchiefs will have overtaken the #34,963 
OL,12,Fannual median wage for full-time       
OL,13,Fworkers, the High Pay Centre says.     
OL,15,FIncluding pensions, top bosses' average
OL,16,Freward amounts to #3.81m per year, the 
OL,17,Fcentre says.                           
OL,19,FThat works out to #1,170 per hour - 109
OL,20,Ftimes the average full-time worker.    
